Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the street, their facades bathed in the soft glow of daylight. Cars and bicycles, parked neatly along the side of the road, add a touch of everyday life to the scene. The sky overhead is a blanket of overcast clouds, casting a muted light over the cityscape. The colors in the image are predominantly green, gray, and brown, reflecting the urban environment and the natural elements within it.
